                                    (<ref xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" href="/hk/cap426">Cap. 426</ref>) then forming part of the
                                scheme’s assets exceeded 5% of the market value or, where
                                appropriate, the net realizable value on such date of the scheme’s
                                assets as a whole) the particulars of the investments and the
                                percentage they then formed of the market value or (where
                                appropriate) the net realizable value.</p>
                        </td>
